    # game/areas/galerocks01structure.rpy:1643
    old "You find her with a few children that are playing tag, watched by two elderly women, most likely twin sisters. Her skin tone, nose, and ears help you recognize her right away, even though her eyes are brown and dark, nothing like the bright green of her father’s. \n\nHer shell may be present, but she stares at the dusty yard, ignored by her group. She’s leaning against the wall, drawing something on the ground with her foot, without a word or a tune. \n\nYou ask the sitters if she’s alright, and their grim eyes are enough of an answer. “A melancholic lass, she is.” You ask if you can talk to her, explaining that her father has been worrying about her lately, and they invite you with a gesture. "
